{
  "text": "This article presents a Bayesian modeling approach to estimate the model parameters and various measures of subject-level predictions. Although not as computationally efficient as the modeling framework in [CITATION_1] , our algorithm remains feasible using modern computing platforms and software. To ensure reproducibility of our results, we have posted our code, simulated data, and results at www.biostat.jhsph.edu/\u223cccrainic/webpage/programs/ smoking/MCMC Luo smoking.zip",
